{"id":619325973,"lang":"cpp","time":"1 month, 4 weeks","timestamp":1642121838,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"6 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/619325973/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"String to Integer (atoi)","memory":"7.2 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int removeSpace(string s){\n        int i=0;\n        while(i<s.size() && s[i]==' ')i++;\n        return i;\n    }\n    int getInt(int i,string s,bool neg){\n        long int ans=0;\n        while(i<s.size() && s[i]>='0' && s[i]<='9'){\n                ans=(ans*10)+(s[i]-'0');\n                if(ans>INT_MAX){\n                    if(neg) return INT_MIN;\n                    return INT_MAX;\n                }   \n            i++;\n        }\n        if(neg) return -1*ans;\n        return ans;\n    }\n    int myAtoi(string s) {\n        int n=s.size();\n        int i=removeSpace(s);\n        bool neg=0;\n        if(s[i]=='+' || s[i]=='-'){\n            if(s[i]=='-') neg=1;\n            i++;\n        }\n        return getInt(i,s,neg);\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"string-to-integer-atoi"}
